name: Grandma Texas
text: Guy's, It was really yummy tonight. Thanks  Papa Murphy's

name: Took Chevy
text: Ran out of mushrooms...? I ordered online 8 hours earlier for their cowboy special. An email or notification of some sort would have been nice before i went to pick it up. Its literally their special. Oh well it was still good, and they let …More

name: vineel kodikanti
text: Some pizza combinations are better than others, but. Pretty good overall. The take and back style can be useful but I think the crusts will not be as good as pizza baked in stores unless you have a good oven at home.

name: Natalie Hardy
text: I love Papa Murphy's Pizza. I usually get the XLM which is a very large pizza that has thin crust. I like I can have fresh and hot pizza right out of the oven. You can call in your order ahead of time or get it made in the store. They even …More

name: Jada Hernandez
text: My first time here, but it looks delicious and the staff was courteous.

name: Caryn Mills
text: Our neighborhood Pappa Murphy's! Mr. Ernie, the manager was great even on a busy Tuesday night.  Everyone worked fast and ensured we got good service.  As usual.

name: Samantha Minardi
text: Ask and you shall receive...just go in and pick out what you want on your pizza ...take it home and bake it in your oven. Enjoy!!

name: Matt Cragg
text: Great food and even better that you get to customize your pizza from scratch

name: Samuel Fowler
text: All you gotta do is tell the workers what to put on your pizza, and bake at home. Good for quick visits when time is squished.

name: Bonnie Cannan
text: The employees are cheerful and patient answering all my silly questions. I love that I can customize the toppings on my pie. I can be very picky, ; ). Their ingredients are good quality. Such a good deal.

name: Anish Patel
text: Never tried it before but wow the stuffed pizza is very good. A bit on the pricey side for pizza.

name: Bob Crimm
text: Tuesdays & Friday cheap pizza but good.

name: Amber McCartney
text: Love Papa Murphy’s! Great pizza, great price, and great customer service & staff!

name: lol lol
text: My favorite store. Ernie manager on duty the best

name: Deborah-Ann Baisch
text: Discovered Papa's when I lived in California. Being an east coast Italian, I was quite skeptical what the quality and taste of the pizza would be like.  I was very pleasantly surprised.  Now that I live in Texas, I turn everybody I know onto Papa's. You just can't beat it for price and selection.

name: Laura Schneider
text: Great Pizza but most of all, outstanding service from Ernie....!

name: Karyn Weiss
text: I like the pizzas here. They have better flavor than all the other places we've tried.

name: Guy Hunter
text: You might want to update your website and maps and everything else since you're no longer open

name: Henry Alvarado
text: Great pies. Take it home and add garlic and onions and whatever I can add thats in the fridge. Delicious!

name: Cindy S
text: Employee was complaining he was left alone to work and wait time was much longer then normal.  Manager needs to do better.

name: george stifflemire III
text: Good place for take out pizza.

name: Janine Ray
text: Love their Tuesday 5 topping large pizza for $10 even!

name: Ally Cone
text: Not that I have a problem with the food, it's this location in particular. I've tried to order from here twice. The first time I made an online order on a Saturday morning. It was to pick up at 11 am, an hour after their posted opening …More

name: H H
text: Delicious pizza For Bake , customers service Amazing as well, highly recommend this place!!!!

name: Ford
text: Pretty good pizza with plenty of choices. Staff was very helpful.

name: Ricardo Portela
text: Great pizza, and you bake it at home (eat it while it's hot). Also you don't pay sales tax since the pizza is not baked.

name: Sonya H
text: Always get great service here.

name: Anthony Shutey
text: Their stuffed crust pizza's are the very best. It is Chicago style at its best

name: Josh Kimbell
text: They give you pizzas to take home and bake. Decent value, and the product is ok.

name: Mark Seymour
text: They make pizza and you bake it, simple, cheap.

name: James R Wilson
text: This place is now closed.

name: Mark Bower
text: They are friendly and it's quick and easy

name: Lea Swanson
text: Loved it and it is the closest one we have found

text: good pizzas here!

name: Curtis Carty
text: My favorite! Can't beat price!
